wb_key_flight_number.description: Primary flight identifier (flight number) used as part of the Waybill/Workbook key.

wb_key_flight_zulu_date.description: Flight date in Zulu/UTC context as provided in source (Excel date string). Example: 12/02/2025.

wb_leg_leg_number.description: Leg sequence number for the flight (e.g., 1 for first leg).

wb_container_position_code.description: Container position code indicating where the container is placed on the aircraft (e.g., '10L').

wb_leg_equipment_code.description: Equipment code for the aircraft/leg (numeric code from source).

wb_leg_aircraft_make_model_description.description: Aircraft make/model description for the leg (e.g., 'B777F').

wb_leg_aircraft_config_series_code.description: Aircraft configuration/series code (single-letter code in sample).

wb_leg_iata_destination_code.description: IATA destination airport code for the leg (e.g., 'MEM').

wb_leg_iata_station_code.description: IATA station code associated with the leg (e.g., 'STN').

wb_leg_master_cons_number.description: Master consolidation number for the leg (identifier string from source).

wb_container_adg_idg_cd.description: Hazmat/commodity classification code indicating ADG/IDG category (single-letter in sample).

wb_container_compartment_location_code.description: Compartment/location code where the container is loaded (numeric string in sample).

wb_container_container_scan_code.description: Scan code associated with the container (identifier string).

wb_container_container_weight.description: Container weight as provided by source system (units not explicitly stated).

wb_container_cube_percent.description: Cube utilization percentage for the container (as a percent value).

wb_container_height_code.description: Container height code (numeric string in sample).

wb_container_iata_container_destination_.description: IATA destination code for the container's destination.

wb_container_iata_package_destination_co.description: IATA destination code for packages within the container (if applicable).

wb_container_load_code.description: Load code describing the load category/type for the container.

wb_container_package_service_code.description: Service code for packages associated with the container.

wb_container_position_remark_description.description: Free-text remark/description about the container position.

wb_container_sequence_number.description: Sequence number for the container record within the leg/flight.

total_pkg_count.description: Total package count associated with the record/container.

bag_count.description: Count of bagged items (bags) in the load.

loose.description: Count of loose items (not bagged) in the load.

bagged.description: Count of bagged items (explicit bagged quantity field).

actual_weight_pkg_count.description: Package count with actual weight data present.

actual_volume_pkg_count.description: Package count with actual volume data present.

est_volume_pkg_count.description: Package count with estimated volume data present.

null_volume_pkg_count.description: Package count where volume is null/missing.

HWT_pkg_count.description: Package count classified as HWT category.

DOC_pkg_count.description: Package count classified as DOC category.

Box_pkg_count.description: Package count classified as BOX category.

HWT_wgt_lb.description: Weight in pounds for HWT category packages.

DOC_wgt_lb.description: Weight in pounds for DOC category packages.

BOX_wgt_lb.description: Weight in pounds for BOX category packages.

HWT_act_volume_cuft.description: Actual volume (cubic feet) for HWT category packages.

DOC_act_volume_cuft.description: Actual volume (cubic feet) for DOC category packages.

BOX_act_volume_cuft.description: Actual volume (cubic feet) for BOX category packages.

HWT_est_volume_cuft.description: Estimated volume (cubic feet) for HWT category packages.

DOC_est_volume_cuft.description: Estimated volume (cubic feet) for DOC category packages.

BOX_est_volume_cuft.description: Estimated volume (cubic feet) for BOX category packages.

ADG_pkg_count.description: Package count classified as ADG (dangerous goods) category.

ADG_volume_cuft.description: Volume (cubic feet) for ADG category packages.

cons_start_datetime_utc.description: Consolidation start datetime in UTC context as provided (string timestamp).

cons_end_datetime_utc.description: Consolidation end datetime in UTC context as provided (string timestamp).

cons_start_datetime_local.description: Consolidation start datetime in local time context as provided (string timestamp).

cons_end_datetime_local.description: Consolidation end datetime in local time context as provided (string timestamp).

cons_create_employee_nbr.description: Employee number(s) associated with creation of the consolidation record (may contain multiple IDs).

LEG_TYPE_CD.description: Leg type code from source (single-letter in sample).

uld_char_uld_avg_tare_wgt.description: Average tare weight for the ULD type (units not explicitly stated).

uld_char_actual_stack_eff_cube.description: Actual stack efficiency cube value for the ULD characteristics.

uld_char_match_rate_cube.description: Match rate cube metric for ULD characteristics.

uld_char_uld_max_weight.description: Maximum allowable weight for the ULD type.

recmd_pos_cube_ft_qty.description: Recommended cube feet quantity for the position.

recmd_pos_watson_uld_cnt_qty.description: Recommended ULD count quantity (Watson/optimizer output as labeled in source).

buildup_globl_rgn_cd.description: Global region code for buildup region (e.g., 'EU').

total_filled_uld_cu_ft.description: Total filled ULD volume in cubic feet.

Total_Pkg_WGT.description: Total package weight (units implied by other fields; not explicitly stated).

VOID_MT_FLAG.description: Flag indicating void/empty condition as provided (e.g., 'N').

acrft_cuft.description: Aircraft available/related cubic feet metric from source.

aircraft_bulk_target.description: Bulk target value for the aircraft/load plan (units not explicitly stated).

Box_tot_volume_cuft.description: Total volume in cubic feet for BOX freight.

DG_Base_FLAG.description: Dangerous goods base flag as provided (e.g., 'N').

Vol_data_Flag.description: Flag indicating volume data status as provided.

Exclusion_Flag.description: Flag indicating exclusion status as provided (e.g., 'N').

net_weight_container.description: Net weight of the container (units not explicitly stated).

DOC_Cuft_calculation.description: Calculated DOC cubic feet value as provided.

total_calculated_cuft.description: Total calculated cubic feet value as provided.

Bulk_opportunity.description: Bulk opportunity metric (value in sample is 0).

bypass_cuft.description: Bypass cubic feet metric (value in sample is 0).

HWT_tot_volume_cuft.description: Total volume in cubic feet for HWT category.
